s are invisible. They guide users effortlessly toward their goals while making complex tasks feel simple. My approach combines user research, data analysis, and creative problem-solving to build products that people actually want to use.","designer_name":"Akib Ahmed","bio_personal":"When I'm not pushing pixels, you'll find me brewing specialty coffee, producing music, or contributing to design communities. I love sharing knowledge and learning from other designers.","projects_completed":50,"cv_url":"#","availability_status":"Currently Available","availability_note":"Open for new projects starting February 2026","trusted_companies":["TechCorp","StartupXYZ","DesignLab","InnovateCo"],"skills":["User Research","Wireframing","Prototyping","UI Design","Design Systems","Usability Testing","Information Architecture","Interaction Design"],"hero_heading_prefix":"I design","hero_heading_suffix":"experiences","whatsapp_number":"+8801843706840","why_work_subtitle":"I combine design thinking with business strategy to create products that users love and companies profit from","process_title":"My Design Process","process_cta_title":"Ready to work together?","process_cta_subtitle":"Let's discuss how my process can help solve your design challenges"}
